item.title: My first
item.dc:creator: @aps aps
item.description:
@aps wrote:

Not trying to be mean but theres a lot that I noticed.

Renders need blending, new backgrounds (try making your own), you really need to cut the renders out a lot better, and the fonts need to kind of just flow.

Also, try to use your name instead of just words.
